Pattern是一个word，words是一个word list
如果word list里面的某个word每个字母加上相同的数字能够ACII-ly等于Pattern，那就必须出现在return里
source: LeetCode890
思路：Canonical Form

function encode(s):
    map = empty dict   // char -> next id
    next_id = 0
    code = empty list
    for ch in s:
        if ch not in map:
            map[ch] = next_id
            next_id += 1
        code.append(map[ch])
    return code
